    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Changed logic significantly:\r\n- capture of node events enabled by default - controlled by CaptureNodeLatencyStatsEventHistory in StatsConfig\r\n- session logging moved to separate component PeerSessionLogger\r\n- session logs are placed in separate files under log dir \\ logEvents directory\r\n- while closing with e, only general session stats are logged - generalStats.log file\r\n- while closing with q, session stats for each node (with more events then NodeDiscovered) are logged in separate files with nodeId as file name\r\n- additionally session stats log can be triggered while app is running with debug_dumpPeerConnectionDetails json rpc method call included in DebugModule",
